Interface MappingResult<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the result
All Known Subinterfaces:
MappingResult.Successful<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
MappingResult.Failure, MappingResult.Lossless, MappingResult.Lossy
public sealed interface MappingResult<T> permits MappingResult.Successful<T>, MappingResult.Failure<T>
Represents the result of a Mapper call.
See Also:
